I CALLED YOU, LIKE, FIVE TIMES?

39:16.660 --> 39:17.558
- I COULDN'T GET A-HOLD
OF OLIVER,

39:17.590 --> 39:20.172
AND THEN I FOUGHT WITH HIM
FOR A WHILE,

39:20.210 --> 39:21.381
AND THEN I TRIED
TO CALL HIM BACK.

39:21.420 --> 39:22.102
THERE'S NO UPDATES?

39:22.150 --> 39:24.527
- NO.

39:35.540 --> 39:37.155
- SURGERY WENT WELL.

39:37.200 --> 39:39.714
HE'S RECOVERING IN THE ICU NOW.

39:39.750 --> 39:42.685
YOU CAN ALL GO VISIT HIM,
BUT JUST FOR A MINUTE, OKAY?

39:42.720 --> 39:44.096
- SO IT'S--IT'S ALL OVER.

39:44.140 --> 39:47.439
- THERE WERE NO COMPLICATIONS
WITH THE BYPASS

39:47.480 --> 39:48.799
OR THE VALVE REPLACEMENT,

39:48.830 --> 39:52.129
SO WE'LL JUST HAVE TO SEE
HOW HE RESPONDS.

39:52.180 --> 39:54.557
HOPEFULLY HIS HEART MUSCLE
WILL GET STRONGER.

39:54.590 --> 39:57.036
CAMILLE, PLEASE DON'T WORRY.

39:57.080 --> 39:58.934
I'LL CHECK IN WITH YOU TOMORROW.

39:58.980 --> 40:01.073
OH, ALL RIGHT, OKAY.
- THANK YOU.

40:01.120 --> 40:05.011
- THANK YOU VERY MUCH.
- GOOD WORK.

40:05.050 --> 40:07.769
- EVERYTHING'S GONNA BE FINE.
- LET'S GO SEE HIM.

40:07.810 --> 40:09.129
- I COULD'VE DEALT WITH THAT
A LOT BETTER.

40:09.160 --> 40:11.913
- SORRY, IT'S MY FAULT.
YOU ALL RIGHT?

40:11.960 --> 40:12.881
- MM-HMM.
- YOU SURE?

40:12.920 --> 40:16.048
- I JUST TWEAKED SOMETHING
RIDING, I THINK.

40:19.240 --> 40:24.758
- I FEEL SO LIGHT AND I MOVE
LIKE A BIRD

40:24.800 --> 40:30.761
HARD AS A ROSE
SHARP AS A WORD

40:35.220 --> 40:40.465
I'M HAPPY

40:40.500 --> 40:45.153
HERE SHE COMES

40:45.200 --> 40:51.161
THERE WE GO

41:03.660 --> 41:09.212
WHEN I DIE
WHERE I GO?

41:09.250 --> 41:14.734
I DON'T KNOW
THROUGH THE SKY MAYBE DOWN LOW

41:14.780 --> 41:19.194
WHICH EVER

41:19.230 --> 41:23.473
IS FOR REAL

41:30.030 --> 41:36.003
OH YEAH

41:49.120 --> 41:54.740
AND I NEVER HIT THE SPRING SO
HARD

41:54.780 --> 41:59.058
A NEW BORN SONG
ON AN OLD GUITAR

41:59.100 --> 42:03.207
AND I KNOW

42:03.240 --> 42:08.303
WHAT IT MEANS TO BE ALIVE
